            <scopecontent id="aspace_15a242779e4576afa7c0740d5a9644b8">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>The series contains letters from Barlow to his wife Ruth Baldwin Barlow in addition to friends and colleagues.  All letters are outgoing unless otherwise noted.  The series also includes two third party letters, from Marie Joseph Paul Yves Roch Gilbert Du Motier, marquis de Lafayette, to Clara Baldwin, and from Presley Neville to Jonathan Russel (enclosed with Neville's letter to Barlow).</p>
            </scopecontent>
